Document: CryptoKey  
Path: godot/classes/class_cryptokey.rst  
Summary: Methods for loading, saving, and checking public/private key status in CryptoKey.  

Method: is_public_only() → bool. Returns true if this CryptoKey only has the public part, and not the private one.  

Method: load(path: String, public_only: bool = false) → Error. Loads a key from path. If public_only is true, only the public key will be loaded. Note: path should be a "*.pub" file if public_only is true, a "*.key" file otherwise.  

Method: load_from_string(string_key: String, public_only: bool = false) → Error. Loads a key from the given string_key. If public_only is true, only the public key will be loaded.  

Method: save(path: String, public_only: bool = false) → Error. Saves a key to the given path. If public_only is true, only the public key will be saved. Note: path should be a "*.pub" file if public_only is true, a "*.key" file otherwise.  

Method: save_to_string(public_only: bool = false) → String. Returns a string containing the key in PEM format. If public_only is true, only the public key will be included.